<HEADLINE>
FT  14 JUN 93 / International Company News: Business Technology Pounds 6m in
red
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
RESTRUCTURED Business Technology Group, which sells and services office
equipment, announced pre-tax losses of Pounds 6.31m for 1992. Losses last
time of Pounds 7.44m have been restated in accordance with FRS 3.
Turnover amounted to Pounds 20.2m (Pounds 42.4m) and the pre-tax result was
after a loss of Pounds 271,000 on disposal of fixed assets, a Pounds 3.82m
loss on the sale or termination of businesses, and Pounds 792,000 of costs
associated with the reorganisation of the group's activities.
Losses per share were 32.7p (38.4p).
</TEXT>
