<HEADLINE>
FT  14 JUN 93 / International Company News: BP France
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
BP France has recommended acceptance of the offer by BP Europe, itself part
of British Petroleum, for the 14.01 per cent of the French company's shares
it does not already own.
The offer price is FFr120 per share, excluding the 1992 dividend. This gives
shareholders a premium of 43 per cent on the last quoted price.
