with Mr Miyazawa.
Meanwhile, it has emerged that the shadowy security council - a committee of
senior officials that deals with foreign and some domestic affairs, in
addition to security - is to be headed by Marshal Yevgeny Shaposhnikov,
previously head of the Commonwealth of Independent States' unified command.
