FT  12 JUN 93 / Exchanges sign surveillance pact
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE LONDON Stock Exchange said yesterday that it and the Securities and
Futures Authority were among 10 exchanges and regulatory organisations in
Europe and north America which have agreed to share information about
securities traded in more than one marketplace.
The 10 are all members of the Intermarket Surveillance Group.
